---
title: Thai Sea Bass with Green Beans and Lime Rice
description: Delicate white fish, red chilli, lime and fresh veggies are gently combined with fresh chopped coriander and ginger for a layer of delicious textures. Fresh, zesty, light and comforting, our Thai sea bass is a guaranteed dinner winner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/thai-sea-bass-b2483b8c-d58e8e94.jpg
